    • Field Detail

      • selection

        public Artificer.Selection selection
        Artifacts this artificer can craft. This generically represents the base components the Artificer has at the moment to create this selection of magic items. Will randomly replace an item once per month, representing not only a possible sell but also getting new alchemical components, old ones spoiling, etc.
